graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v-2160-148]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|core platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.28+]
    KubeRay -->|operator framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.16.3]
    KubeRay -->|OpenShift routes| OpenshiftAPI[OpenShift API]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler v1.6.0-alpha]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS fault tolerance| Redis[External Redis]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS fault tolerance| S3[S3-Compatible Storage]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|CRD integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    KubeRay -->|metrics export| MonStack[Monitoring Stack]
    KubeRay -->|access control| RBAC[Kubernetes/OpenShift RBAC]

    %% Integration Points (Outbound)
    KubeRay -->|pod/service mgmt| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    KubeRay -->|certificate mgmt| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>optional]

    %% Integration Points (Inbound)
    UserKubectl[Users via kubectl] -->|creates CRs| KubeRay
    Dashboard -->|UI management| KubeRay
    APIServerOpt[APIServer<br/>optional] -.->|HTTP/gRPC API| KubeRay

    %% Ray Framework Dependencies
    RayPods[Ray Pods<br/>Head + Workers] -->|coordination| RayGCS[Ray GCS<br/>port 6379]
    RayPods -->|dashboard/jobs| RayDashboard[Ray Dashboard<br/>port 8265]
    RayPods -->|serving| RayServe[Ray Serve<br/>port 8000]

    KubeRay -->|manages lifecycle| RayPods

    %% External access
    ExternalClients[External Clients] -->|HTTPS/443| OpenshiftRoutes[OpenShift Routes]
    OpenshiftRoutes -->|HTTP/8265 or 8000| RayPods

    %% Monitoring flows
    Prometheus -.->|scrapes :8080| KubeRay
    Prometheus -.->|scrapes :8080| RayPods
    MonStack -.->|collects| Prometheus

